{"id":394471,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/【图说天朝】红包数额也敏感/","date":"2015-06-04T02:11:37Z","modified":"2015-06-04T02:11:37Z","title":"【图说天朝】红包数额也敏感","content":"<p>6月3日晚间，有网友在微信试图向朋友发送数额为6.4元人民币的红包，系统提示“交易异常，请稍后再试”，发送失败。后经网友测试，89.64、64.89、8.9、6.4、0.89等数额均不能发送。很明显，这一乌龙设定与6月4日的敏感日有关。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGkiHinUQAA46Jn.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-394472\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGkiHinUQAA46Jn.png\" alt=\"CGkiHinUQAA46Jn\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGkiHinUQAA46Jn.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGkiHinUQAA46Jn-169x300.png 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGkiHinUQAA46Jn-576x1024.png 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGkiH6SUIAA64BV.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-394473\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGkiH6SUIAA64BV.png\" alt=\"CGkiH6SUIAA64BV\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGkiH6SUIAA64BV.png 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGkiH6SUIAA64BV-169x300.png 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGlmm7-UgAEKJfG.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-394474\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGlmm7-UgAEKJfG.jpg\" alt=\"CGlmm7-UgAEKJfG\" width=\"450\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGlmm7-UgAEKJfG.jpg 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/CGlmm7-UgAEKJfG-180x300.jpg 180w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>majunspace：腾讯旗下的微信红包禁止六块四，六十四，把自己搞得跟国企一样。不过诸如新浪淘宝这些企业，表面是新兴民营科技，实质还是落后体系的一部分。</p>\n<p>rbttt：( ´◔ ‸◔‘)我说微信不能发64，6.4元红包。却还是有两个傻孩子，一个给我发了6.4支付宝，一个给我微信转账6.4元…</p>\n<p>beidaijin：再接这里：刚有测试相关内容的用户表示，自己在微信红包祝福语中填写「八九六四」字样，被自动修改为「恭喜发财」。</p>\n<p>Jwong1202：已测试的确如此，土共疯了。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1003,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[19985,27767,27918,27919]}